reviews.review_text: Absolute ripper Fantastic show, really hits liftoff in Set 2 with the Playin > Wharf Rat > GDTRFB > Playin. Donna is at her absolute best, very soulful and rich. Even the Around & Around (usually a skip for me) is amazing.
